---
description: Run Python tests, benchmarks, and examples in the qgd conda environment
alwaysApply: true
---

For this repository, run Python for **tests**, **benchmarks**, and **examples** with the **qgd** conda environment, e.g. `conda run -n qgd python -m pytest …` or activate `qgd` first. Do not assume the system or default `python` matches project dependencies.

See also `docs/density_matrix_project/SETUP.md` and `.cursor/rules/RULE.md` for broader build and setup guidance.
